{"tid":817762,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[電解水機] 有冇人知道部機漏緊啲咩","createTime":"2018-09-13T14:53:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T13:31:07.000Z","uid":23873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"630a75fcb71dd19a5b80b2a71c82290ca2322ef6","tid":817762,"uid":23873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T14:53:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/13/224740_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F13%2F224740_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=66d69676&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/13/224752_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F13%2F224752_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ccb1359b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/13/224804_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F13%2F224804_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=c219bab0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n部Panasonic電解水機都用咗五六年<br />\n早兩個星期開始部機底個去露水位係咁漏啲黐立立好似機油嘅嘢<br />\n但啲水又好似冇咩事仲飲得<br />\n屋企人又好似當冇事咁<br />\n應該等緊我出錢換過部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人知係咩黎<br />\n啲水會唔會飲死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aa59b8991c1a943a44a5e1889992a96a3a16830","tid":817762,"uid":175896,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T14:54:46.000Z","msg":"搬啦 搞唔掂架喇"},{"pid":"54253db913459fa8d07f1b54b8ae6572ad383d80","tid":817762,"uid":2950,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T14:55:28.000Z","msg":"血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66cb02446fbefb665e8ba0a9337f9e6d5e5ea4fe","tid":817762,"uid":155